{"tid":312164,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［季後鳥］Nike+apps人體實驗測試","createTime":"2017-07-07T08:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T14:02:04.000Z","uid":77696,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd5dfdf44d975782d9a5eeca3014954cb9dd51f","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"實不相瞞，做左所謂廢青幾個月，加上個人無點郁嘅情況，個人身體嘅負面野開始浮哂出黎，無論心理上同生理都係，即係d人成日話人個樣好唔「正能樣」咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係心理層面上：抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，情緒長期低落，對事物失去興趣同動力，唔想同人講野，思想負面等等.....（我估好多人明我講咩）<br />\n<br />\n係生理層面上....我唔講咁多，我用圖片黎答你<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/154822_4231ae37e40eba664a2fbb5870157b97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F154822_4231ae37e40eba664a2fbb5870157b97.jpg&h=458281c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/154822_4f3c3f6a717446047a78b373b83c3687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F154822_4f3c3f6a717446047a78b373b83c3687.jpg&h=650bdbf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始有涼背，大肚腩，圓肩，扁平足，O型腳，腰痛等等等....<br />\n以上生理問題就促進左其他心理問題喇（我估）<br />\n例如：身體機能差左，咁抵抗地心吸力就困難左，自然動力就會少左，心理上就可能覺得自己老左or能力弱左嘅感覺出現，但可能實際上並不如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又例如.....唔好講咁遠，你個肚腩大左咪覺得自己染羅，講咁複雜做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好！正有此推論，所以想令自己無咁負面嘅方法就做運動喇！let's go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似發現新大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n但係.....我又唔係運動員，運動係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n依個問題相當容易解決，就係去download <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/160529_7f0382068ebdbb661c5f30e497164124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F160529_7f0382068ebdbb661c5f30e497164124.jpg&h=8f6066f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNike+training club 喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eac56135eae5b18ddcfa61ba38ddcea5b1c9574","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"只需要申請完acc，入埋自己身高體重就得架喇，依個apps就好嘅係，你弱智到連plan都唔洗plan，因為已經有哂唔同種類嘅計劃，只有你做定唔做架啫。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話，「我屋企無啞鈴，點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」<br />\nSor，依個app係會斗把琴醒你嘅，因為做運動係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔需要器械嘅</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/161156_753e854cff2fe536eb6a8225dec70613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F161156_753e854cff2fe536eb6a8225dec70613.jpg&h=5d1ff2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/160856_0364037d5243d4a4a30752a926788cf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F160856_0364037d5243d4a4a30752a926788cf2.jpg&h=161c0af0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f3808d7b81d34f360c8ccdf9c113f65fa6e4105","tid":312164,"uid":16036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a1ad46d7ac9d44d4fc21fd728578ccfeba328c70","tid":312164,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"完全征伐呢個PLAN 係未現代帝皇術嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ab1f8a6b02761a1c3bcde5c12e8bcbafc1b4d6","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/162715_490602ca05b993648f8703506e9d9a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F162715_490602ca05b993648f8703506e9d9a12.jpg&h=fa1faf4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個實驗就係咁，我set左4個星期訓練，睇下做完之後分別有幾大<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/163158_c3049d031d82bef125745e6a89f91c5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F163158_c3049d031d82bef125745e6a89f91c5f.jpg&h=05236cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人當然要挑戰自己！（查實有d不自量力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/163358_72be785057added04f8e4b1ccf8a2912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F163358_72be785057added04f8e4b1ccf8a2912.jpg&h=37cc8902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做就好簡單嘅啫⋯⋯咪跟住做羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1750338aea2e6f0ce70d22c121f927bf6d1c2e7","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全征伐呢個PLAN 係未現代帝皇術嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帝唔帝就唔知，不過做完就真係濕到好現代"},{"pid":"ea8398e8e6269217453b2508bc5a5b6d04f26194","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"Day1: 7月7號<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/170712_b5f1e8db6a51e8360011d0d4e1cde39d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F170712_b5f1e8db6a51e8360011d0d4e1cde39d.jpg&h=8e6e5ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本琴日諗住計6點起身，可惜番訓先係人生最大敵人，失敗左，唔緊（都無得話緊唔緊）<br />\n起身即做<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nfT0RB0cVz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnfT0RB0cVz8&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b4a5fe74\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nfT0RB0cVz8</a><br />\n麻煩腦內補完，自行幫個樣打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日做嘅大部份係胸同腳嘅訓練<br />\n做到大半有少量偷雞情況出現，但......情有可原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高度推薦放定一公升水係旁邊，因為做完之後個地下好似賴尿咁<br />\n瑜伽墊都是必須，因為依加下下骨頭撞地板，唔係地下穿就骨頭斷<br />\n<br />\n明天繼續"},{"pid":"da535a14e3500d82da5ec7969055b7d6aef1bf52","tid":312164,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"做gym la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594cc286de1f17ee05596876318529e09de7df4c","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:03:32.000Z","msg":"Day2 7月8號<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-DeaUArSq9U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-DeaUArSq9U&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4774dbdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-DeaUArSq9U</a><br />\n依舊係6點起唔到身，<br />\n今日依然係做完全征服<br />\n7月7號做完之後已經2腳酸痛<br />\n所以做到第30分鐘就無做<br />\n<br />\nBtw點解影到股溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232f51f43531b08c74f93a65fb82b1962e0b91b5","tid":312164,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"正正經經去健身室，請教下其他人仲好啦，係到玩自學，仲要徒手既添。不過無人阻止到你既，而且你繼續咁做都可能或者減到肥既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceeda546c338f3ba0c5090cd1297909359e8050b","tid":312164,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/133442_f240687c7e5c7039975c33f3f18e1d0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F133442_f240687c7e5c7039975c33f3f18e1d0f.jpg&h=f4ac5ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n系開芯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0312bc51179752d6569675c4e053c92bfa23aab6","tid":312164,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野,跑下步算啦"},{"pid":"906a08a9334390dcacf2080a99391ce59961c750","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正正經經去健身室，請教下其他人仲好啦，係到玩自學，仲要徒手既添。不過無人阻止到你既，而且你繼續咁做都可能或者減到肥既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係純粹想比人睇下係無gym room下跟Nike app做睇下做成點，因為我相信依樣野係人人都得，最緊要有心"},{"pid":"1213fb3373a42c2d42f677fb4a56cf20a7cdc562","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好搞咁多野,跑下步算啦</blockquote>個計劃有跑架，我只係跟住做"},{"pid":"ddf034eef53baa0e656f35a63ce14bafb3233217","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/133442_f240687c7e5c7039975c33f3f18e1d0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F133442_f240687c7e5c7039975c33f3f18e1d0f.jpg&h=f4ac5ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n系開芯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多個冷仔唷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95725994e7d979a7ed90afe5f2bb9d1ecde006b","tid":312164,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正正經經去健身室，請教下其他人仲好啦，係到玩自學，仲要徒手既添。不過無人阻止到你既，而且你繼續咁做都可能或者減到肥既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地有心做就得啦<br />\n下下都要去做gym咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d200e81e81137eed70d1c80da4b47ddd113a4fd","tid":312164,"uid":67317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好搞咁多野,跑下步算啦</blockquote><br />\n跑步減肥依個概念都幾落後下"},{"pid":"877349c18c19b706e60e5c8c4f7d88cd6da651e4","tid":312164,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"87cf50658655b6141f778dceae4708cae799c934","tid":312164,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"7月8號條片<br />\n0:14你半個屎忽走左出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba07feed63748e5efadf9e72412b4c31a4b7151","tid":312164,"uid":2477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:52:15.000Z","msg":"你呢個post超撚正"},{"pid":"9e701e5c641ded20c6ae0eed2137bfe737ad0b31","tid":312164,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗夾錢買條緊少少既短褲比樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7ce3249a087b5ec0493a035c2ef98331809807","tid":312164,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗夾錢買條緊少少既短褲比樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a68710c15d8c5e89e3a604b5026d758f94e5e25","tid":312164,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗夾錢買條緊少少既短褲比樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31e31d8ff0d1140f2267768acaaa051804ed631","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗夾錢買條緊少少既短褲比樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af2a125dbf819ffbc230985a02efe639b860237","tid":312164,"uid":77696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"7月9號<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/atQ8uKgvHDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FatQ8uKgvHDg&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d91de145\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/atQ8uKgvHDg</a><br />\n今日終於成功起早左2個鐘頭身，8點就起左喇，雖然起身之後都係係張床到禁手機，但我感到離成功不遠。<br />\n<br />\n好，今日個apps叫我跑30分鐘，易過借火啦，最後以跑5分鐘抖10分鐘嘅姿態完成。<br />\n明天繼續"}]}